Our solution is an AI-powered online marketplace that helps local artisans sell their products easily.  Artisans just upload a photo of their product, and the AI automatically writes a good description, sets the right price, and shows it to the right customers.  Customers get personalized recommendations, can ask questions through a chatbot in their own language, and even verify that the product is authentic and handmade.  This way, artisans save time, reach more buyers, and earn fairly, while customers enjoy a trustworthy and personalized shopping experience.
